bar Ali Khan Sikander Jah, Asaf Jah III|Sikandar Jah]] |- | [[Armavir, Armenia|Sardarabad]] <small>(present-day [[Armavir, Armenia|Armavir]]) </small>|| {{flag|Armenia}}|| |- | [[Türkmenabat]]|| {{flag|Turkmenistan}}||[[Turkmens]] |- | [[Vagharshapat]]|| {{flag|Armenia}}|| Prince Vardges Manouk |- | [[Aurangabad, Maharashtra|Aurangabad]]||{{flag|India}}||[[Aurangzeb]] |}
